data.description: Discover this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home nestled in the desirable community of American Heritage Estates, and the best part? No HOA! Step inside to find a well-designed split floor plan adorned with tile flooring in the living areas and laminate wood flooring in the bedrooms. The kitchen boasts elegant granite counters, perfect for culinary adventures. Outside, a spacious fenced backyard awaits, complete with a sprawling 30x10 covered lanai, ideal for outdoor gatherings. Plus, enjoy the peace of mind provided by the 7 year old roof and water heater. Come and experience this fantastic home for yourself!
